v0.4.0 (2012-04-12)

  - support for multiple Adobe Connect instances
  

v0.3.0 (2011-06-02)

  - option to use one time passwords when logging to Adobe Connect server
  - option to refresh user data (first name, surname, email) on every login
  - option to create user accounts on the Adobe Connect server, if they don't exist (it was hard-coded in the previous version)
  - improved logging
  - Zend Framework v1.11.6


v0.2.0 (2009-04-01)

  - option to add newly created users to a default group (must exist at the server)
  - option to pass a 'target' GET variable with a specific URL users should be redirected to after login


v0.1.0 (2009-03-10)

  - initial version
  - basic functionality
  - supports Shibboleth authentication only
  - supports Adobe Connect 6+
  - requires PHP 5.2+, Zend Framework 1.5+ and AC PHP API
